getViews

public java.util.Collection<ViewInfo> getViews(java.lang.String componentId)
Description copied from interface: ComponentProvider
Provides the view roles for the component type. This allows views to be added for any component type, including those that were supplied by another provider to extend a component's view. The platform will attempt to provide default views where possible (currently this provides NodeViewRole, HousingViewRole, and CanvasViewRole instances) so these roles do not need to be provided by the developer unless the default functionality is inadequate.

Specified by:
getViews in interface ComponentProvider
Parameters:
componentId - to supply view roles for
Returns:
non null collection of view roles that should be applied to the current component
